life: 0.1
name: cloudflare
summary: Infrastructure adapter for Cloudflare Workers

provides:
  - infra.compute
  - infra.datastore
  - infra.kv
  - infra.object_store
  - infra.route
  - infra.cron
  - infra.queue
  - infra.secret_store

commands:
  connect:
    run: node connect.js
  smokecheck:
    run: node smokecheck.js
  deploy:
    run: node deploy.js

checks:
  - node connect.js --check

secrets:
  - CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN
  - CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID

---

# Cloudflare Adapter

Translates Life capabilities to Cloudflare resources:
- infra.compute → Worker
- infra.datastore → D1
- infra.kv → KV namespace
- infra.object_store → R2 bucket
- infra.route → custom domain / route
- infra.cron → Cron Trigger
- infra.queue → Queue
- infra.secret_store → Worker Secrets

Connection reads CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN and CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID
from environment. Run `life run cloudflare.connect` to verify.
